      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. The engine and transmission are fully functional, but please be aware of some minor fluid seeping and a bit of noise during cold starts. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some light staining on the carpets. It has been maintained well enough to stay on the road, but a new owner should expect to invest in some minor repairs and cosmetic touch-ups in the near future.",
