    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies both mechanical integrity and aesthetic sophistication. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, this unit offers a seamless balance of performance and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a commendable finish, complemented by a well-preserved interior cabin that reflects a high standard of previous ownership. This vehicle represents an outstanding acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a premium experience and proven durability.",
      "price": 36500.0,
