    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. It\u2019s super reliable, runs great, and is ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
